data.description: Motivated Seller will assist with closing cost. Located in the Garden District of Plaquemine, you will FALL IN LOVE with the balance of how this charming home has keep is original character alive while also modernizing it for today's family.  Most of the home's exterior details are keep intact while inside fresh white paint highlights the house's original beauty including wood floors, molding, doors, windows, transoms, 4 fireplaces (one working) and many other preserved details.  New master bedroom en-suite was added and offers dual vanities and huge master closet. Hall bath was updated and walk-in closets were added to additional bedrooms. New outside ac unit and approx. 8 year old roof. No flood insurance required. Call for our private showing today!
